1
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:43,640
I'm really happy today

2
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:49,320
Oh, right

3
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:55,560
First, I need to find my parents

4
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,280
a place to stay

5
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Where'd you get this money?

6
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:05,400
I took some bags and jewelry I don't use

7
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:05,879
and sold them.

8
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:08,719
I-I can't take this money

9
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,159
Just take it

10
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:11,519
My family's problems

11
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,680
I'll handle them myself

12
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,200
Xiaobei

13
00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:19,519
I know you'll achieve great things someday

14
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:20,920
But the issues at home right now

15
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,840
still need to be dealt with

16
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,920
This money

17
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,439
treat it as a loan from me

18
00:01:28,079 --> 00:01:29,319
No, I can't take it

19
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,159
Put it away, quick

20
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:31,560
Trust me

21
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,439
It'll all be over soon

22
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,159
Go home now

23
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,319
Okay

24
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:52,000
Then I'll

25
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,519
head home

26
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,680
I'm sorry, Si Qi

27
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,759
For my family

28
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,080
I have to leave

29
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:18,879
Hurry, hurry, hurry

30
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:32,159
If you don't want others stepping on you

31
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:34,759
you've gotta step on them first

32
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,199
Give it to Mom, give it to Mom.

33
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,400
I'll do it

34
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:13,800
Come on, come on

35
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,439
What, having regrets?

36
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,000
It was my choice

37
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,280
I don't regret it

38
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,400
Every choice comes with a price

39
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,639
Here, put it on the floor

40
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,039
No matter what

41
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:35,800
I still have to thank you

42
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,599
for renting a place for my family

43
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,479
and lending us money

44
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,599
It's only right

45
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,159
I'll do what I promised you

46
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,360
I hope you will too

47
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,400
Don't worry

48
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,439
I won't let the price I've paid

49
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,000
go to waste

50
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,240
As for me,

51
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,520
I keep money and feelings separate

52
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,360
I won't, simply because you're my son,

53
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,919
hand Prosperity Group over to you

54
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:56,680
Whoever inherits Prosperity Group

55
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,120
has to be capable

56
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,400
I know

57
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,159
You've never believed in my ability

58
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,199
So I hope

59
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,759
you can give me an assessment opportunity

60
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,360
If I can pass your test

61
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,639
then please give me

62
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:08,319
a chance to take over Prosperity Group someday

63
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,080
It's rare to see you this determined

64
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,719
I'll think it over carefully

65
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,000
Oh, right

66
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,199
Financial King of Singapore's daughter,

67
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,600
Lisa, will visit our group tomorrow

68
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,240
You will receive her personally

69
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,079
Yes

70
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,040
And it's a good chance to show

71
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,800
your excellent Malay skills

72
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,879
Sheng Yuanzhou can speak Malay too?

73
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,720
Welcome, Miss Lisa

74
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,120
to Prosperity Group

75
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,519
This is my father

76
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:00,160
It's a pleasure to meet you

77
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:03,759
I'll show you around Prosperity Group

78
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,079
Please follow me

79
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,480
This is Prosperity Group's headquarters

80
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,680
The whole building belongs to the group

81
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,519
I don't have time

82
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:33,839
I've got work tomorrow

83
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,319
How much can you make in a day?

84
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,680
Two hundred at most

85
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,600
Who are you looking down on?

86
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,160
Two hundred fifty

87
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,480
I'll give you four times that

88
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,639
One thousand a day. You in or not?

89
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:50,519
Boss, just tell me what you need

90
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,240
Yuanzhou

91
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,879
Father

92
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,519
That's rude

93
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,040
Yes

94
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,160
You two carry on

95
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,360
I'll head back to my office

96
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,000
Goodbye

97
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,120
Take care, Father

98
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:44,040
Should we keep talking?

99
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:55,240
I'm telling you

100
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,600
it's stuffy and hot in this car

101
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,160
If I'd known it would be this hard,

102
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,439
you should've paid me more

103
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,240
Why aren't you saying anything?

104
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,000
Get in, hurry!

105
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,600
Drive, hurry!

106
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:19,639
Drive, hurry up

107
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,399
What's going on?

108
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,800
We almost blew it

109
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,120
Where are you taking me?

110
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,959
You can speak Chinese?

111
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,040
Of course

112
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,879
My family's from Fujian

113
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,639
Then why did you make me translate?

114
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,839
Looks like it was a test

115
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:48,439
What?

116
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:51,000
I want to go

117
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,959
somewhere with rich Chinese culture

118
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,639
Translator turned driver

119
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,319
Still one thousand a day

120
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,519
You in or not?

121
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,040
No

122
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,839
I don't want him to be just a driver

123
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,720
You

124
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:06,720
be my tour guide

125
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:08,839
Looks like the sponsor picked you

126
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:11,600
My translating job is already done

127
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,639
If you want me as your tour guide

128
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,480
well, then...

129
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,199
you'll have to pay more.

130
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:17,680
You're obsessed with money

131
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:18,959
Your family is loaded

132
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:19,800
and you're still haggling over this?

133
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:21,079
Fine, okay

134
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,639
As long as you take good care of Miss Lisa

135
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,040
I'll pay you double

136
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,519
Let's go, hurry, hurry

137
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,319
Deal

138
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:29,560
Bosses, sit tight

139
00:08:42,279 --> 00:08:43,480
Not done browsing yet?

140
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,120
She's got way too much energy.

141
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:49,240
Keep the young lady happy,

142
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:50,600
and there's money to be made.

143
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,440
I'm all about providing good service.

144
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:54,120
Go on.

145
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,159
The reeds are lush and green,

146
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:00,960
the white dew is now frost.

147
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:03,279
The one I long for

148
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,440
is on the other side of the water.

149
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,639
This...

150
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,600
is the mood from the Book of Songs.

151
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,480
Didn't think you knew poetry.

152
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,200
This spot's called By the Water's Side.

153
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,639
And the Autumn Water and Reed Pavilion

154
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:17,799
faces it directly across the windows,

155
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:18,799
complementing each other.

156
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:22,759
It's not like I only know how to have fun.

157
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,879
I came back to China

158
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:27,799
exactly for this kind of poetic beauty.

159
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:31,159
But this "By the Water's Side"...

160
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:34,200
That out-of-reach feeling's too sad.

161
00:09:34,399 --> 00:09:35,519
I want something more festive.

162
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,919
Festive?

163
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,200
If you want festive,

164
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,240
there's no holiday right now.

165
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,720
Unless... a wedding?

166
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:45,120
This must be fate!

167
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,320
How'd you know?

168
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,000
I've even got a Chinese wedding gown ready.

169
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,360
This is it.

170
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,600
I'll wear this outfit.

171
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:09,679
Which of you's gonna be my bride?

172
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:15,879
You go.

173
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,639
Why me?

174
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,720
I'm paying. Hurry up.

175
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,039
Fine.

176
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,799
Let's go get married.

177
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,080
Zhang Xiaobei.

178
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,360
Si Qi.

179
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,200
What are you doing here?

180
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,320
What are you doing?

181
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,480
I...

182
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,159
Who is she?

183
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:40,960
She's...

184
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,480
The bride.

185
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:45,840
I'm his bride.

186
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:46,960
No!

187
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:47,840
She's an Overseas Chinese.

188
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,600
Her Chinese isn't good.

189
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:52,200
We're going to get married.

190
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,720
My Chinese is great.

191
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,879
Hello. Who are you?

192
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,120
I am...

193
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,639
Don't listen to her nonsense.

194
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,919
I just took a job.

195
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,759
She's a guest of Prosperity Group.

196
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,159
I'm in charge of hosting her.

197
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:06,840
Sheng Yuanzhou.

198
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,480
Explain yourself.

199
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,200
Didn't you say it yourself,

200
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,399
that you were going to get married?

201
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,120
You're kicking me when I'm down, huh?

202
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,399
If you're going to be like this, I quit.

203
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:17,799
Give the money back.

204
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:20,120
What you paid was for translating.

205
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,000
Do you two hate me that much?

206
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,519
No, we don't.

207
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:26,279
Then who's gonna be my bride?

208
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,519
Who's it gonna be?

209
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:50,159
Are you done?

210
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,759
Yeah, let me see.

211
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,919
What are you laughing at?

212
00:12:00,639 --> 00:12:01,919
Nothing. You're really pretty.

213
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:04,200
You'd be even prettier with longer hair.

214
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,720
The weather's so nice today.

215
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,840
How about we take a group photo?

216
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:09,480
Sure.

217
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,039
Let's take one together.

218
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:17,799
Come on.

219
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:18,960
Okay.

220
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,120
Come on.

221
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,519
Let me see.

222
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,480
Why are you eating this junk food?

223
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,759
The news just reported it.

224
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,080
It's made from animal feed.

225
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:40,799
Don't eat it then.

226
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,840
Who said I'm not eating it?

227
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:48,440
Wonder who it was back in school...

228
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,840
who was blown away by starch sausage.

229
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,120
The one blown away...

230
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:26,799
I think that was you.

231
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:31,440
Looks like your memories switched back.

232
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,200
Just eat already.

233
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:38,200
How is it?

234
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,519
Thanks. Bye-bye.

235
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,600
My dad...

236
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,559
My dad woke up.
